                    <li><a href="#" class="font-paragraph text-[16px] leading-paragraph text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Blood Tests</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#" class="font-paragraph text-[16px] leading-paragraph text-gray-300 hover:text-white transition-colors">Pathology</a></li>
